---
import FloatingText from './FloatingText.astro';

const springsImageUrl =
  'https://res.cloudinary.com/sagyo/image/upload/v1709147268/web/ryokan_okunoyu_e6ifmv.webp';
const bambooImageUrl =
  'https://res.cloudinary.com/sagyo/image/upload/v1709159195/web/bamboo_gxwmbl.webp';
---

<Fragment>
  <h3
    class='col-span-12 mb-12 mt-32 font-hanamin text-[clamp(2rem,3.75rem,4vw)] text-japanese-light -lg:text-[min(7vw,3.75rem)]'
  >
    hot springs
  </h3>
  <div class='col-span-4 flex flex-col gap-8 -lg:col-span-12 -lg:mb-12'>
    <p class='max-w-xs -lg:max-w-none'>
      <b>Hot springs</b>, also known as <b>onsen</b> in Japan, are natural geothermal pools that contain
      warm, mineral-rich water. They are believed to offer a range of health benefits, including
      relaxation, improved circulation and relief from aches and pains.
    </p>
    <p class='max-w-xs -lg:max-w-none'>
      You can soak in the hot springs, either indoor or outdoor, and experience their relaxing and
      rejuvenating effects.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class='col-span-8 h-fit w-full border-2 border-japanese-light/35 -lg:col-span-12'>
    <img class='aspect-[4/3] object-cover brightness-75' src={springsImageUrl} alt='' />
  </div>
  <div class='relative col-span-12 mt-12 w-full'>
    <div class='border-2 border-japanese-light/35 -lg:hidden'>
      <img
        class='aspect-[5/1] object-cover brightness-[0.55] saturate-[0.8]'
        src={bambooImageUrl}
        alt=''
      />
    </div>
    <FloatingText
      variant='orange'
      class='bottom-1/2 h-max translate-y-2/3 items-end -lg:translate-y-1/3'
    >
      スパリゾート &nbsp; &nbsp; スパリゾート
      <br />あなたの魂を休 &nbsp; &nbsp; あなたの魂を休
      <br />を休ませる &nbsp; &nbsp; を休ませる
      <br />あなたの &nbsp; &nbsp; あなたの
    </FloatingText>
  </div>
</Fragment>
